name: Retro Sci-Fi
description:
Experimental, unfinished model, on which I will continue to work.

It imitates the style of space artists, 60-70s.

In particular, Andrey Sokolov, Evgeny Leonov, Chesley Bonestell, Paul Calle and some others.

The model is unstable, but many of the results impressed me.

Operating range 0.5-0.9

modelVersions.name: v3
modelVersions.description:
Final version. Trained on paintings from the 70s-80s at a resolution of 512x768.

Problems that exist.

- a large number of objects (you need one ship, 2-3 are generated)

- not always correct understanding of queries (planet, surface of the planet)

I work in the range (0.6-0.7) the higher the value, the stronger the styling.
